name: Nihilistic VAO crew
desc:
Members of the VA Operation have developed a rather unique outlook on life and death. They are unafraid to push their ships beyond what safety protocols would allow, but also don't worry too much when it all inevitably breaks.

Increases the damage and flux cost of energy weapon by %s but reduces the rate broken weapons are repaired by %s.

name: VAO refit
desc: Minor improvements and changes were made to this ship in the docks of the Debajo Del Sol station. This improves ship speed by %s and flux dissipation by %s, while the ship has %s less armor and hull.
